{
  "id": "primary_1_semester_1",
  "title": "小学一年级 · 上学期 — 初次上学",
  "author": "像素校园",
  "characters": [
    { "id": "narrator", "name": "" },
    { "id": "protagonist", "name": "" },
    { "id": "xiaowei", "name": "小维" },
    { "id": "xiaokang", "name": "小康" },
    { "id": "teacher_wang", "name": "王老师" },
    { "id": "xiaoming", "name": "小明" },
    { "id": "xiaohong", "name": "小红" }
  ],
  "chapters": [
    {
      "id": "ch1_opening",
      "title": "开学第一天",
      "background": "backgrounds/school_gate_morning",
      "bgm": "bgm/gentle_morning",
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "id": "op_1",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "九月一日，晴。",
          "effects": [{ "type": "fadeIn", "duration": 1.0 }]
        },
        {
          "id": "op_2",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "阳光透过树叶洒在校门口的石板路上。今天是开学的第一天，也是我人生中第一次踏进小学的校门。"
        },
        {
          "id": "op_3",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "背上的新书包有点沉，但更多的是一种说不清的兴奋。"
        },
        {
          "id": "op_4",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "…好大的学校。操场上好多小朋友。"
        },
        {
          "id": "op_5",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "一个扎着双马尾的女孩蹦蹦跳跳地跑过来，脸上挂着大大的笑容。",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "hasFlag", "key": "protagonist_male" }]
        },
        {
          "id": "op_5b",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "一个手里拿着铅笔盒的男孩腼腆地走过来，冲我笑了笑。",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "hasFlag", "key": "protagonist_female" }]
        },
        {
          "id": "op_6",
          "speaker": "xiaowei",
          "speakerName": "小维",
          "text": "嗨！你也是一年级的吗？我叫小维！",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "hasFlag", "key": "protagonist_male" }]
        },
        {
          "id": "op_6b",
          "speaker": "xiaokang",
          "speakerName": "小康",
          "text": "你…你好。我叫小康。我们是一个班的吗？",
          "emotion": "shy",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "hasFlag", "key": "protagonist_female" }]
        },
        {
          "id": "op_7",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "你好！我叫…",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text": "热情地自我介绍",
              "jumpTo": "op_8_friendly",
              "actions": [{ "type": "affection", "key": "childhood_friend", "value": 2 }]
            },
            {
              "text": "有点害羞，小声说",
              "jumpTo": "op_8_shy",
              "actions": [{ "type": "affection", "key": "childhood_friend", "value": 1 }]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "op_8_friendly",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "你好！我叫[name]！以后一起玩吧！",
          "jumpTo": "op_9"
        },
        {
          "id": "op_8_shy",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "我叫[name]…嗯…请多关照。",
          "jumpTo": "op_9"
        },
        {
          "id": "op_9",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "就这样，我认识了第一个朋友。我们刚好被分在了同一个班级——一年三班。",
          "actions": [{ "type": "setFlag", "key": "met_childhood_friend" }]
        },
        {
          "id": "op_10",
          "speaker": "teacher_wang",
          "speakerName": "王老师",
          "text": "同学们好，我是你们的班主任王老师。欢迎来到一年三班！",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "op_11",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "王老师的声音很温柔，让人觉得很安心。她给每个人发了新课本，书本上还飘着淡淡的印刷味儿。"
        },
        {
          "id": "op_12",
          "speaker": "teacher_wang",
          "speakerName": "王老师",
          "text": "从今天开始，你们就是小学生啦。要好好相处，一起学习，一起长大哦。"
        },
        {
          "id": "op_13",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "我的小学生活，就这样开始了。",
          "effects": [{ "type": "fadeOut", "duration": 1.0 }],
          "actions": [{ "type": "setFlag", "key": "school_started" }]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ch1_first_week",
      "title": "第一周 · 认识同桌",
      "background": "backgrounds/classroom",
      "bgm": "bgm/daily_school",
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "id": "fw_1",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "开学第一周过得飞快。王老师给大家排了座位，我被安排在靠窗的第二排。",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "hasFlag", "key": "school_started" }]
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_2",
          "speaker": "teacher_wang",
          "speakerName": "王老师",
          "text": "今天我们来选班长。想当班长的小朋友请举手哦。",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_3",
          "speaker": "xiaohong",
          "speakerName": "小红",
          "text": "老师！我！",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_4",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "前排一个扎马尾的女孩高高举起手，眼睛亮晶晶的。她就是小红，后来的班长。"
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_5",
          "speaker": "xiaoming",
          "speakerName": "小明",
          "text": "我我我！我也要当！",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_6",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "旁边一个虎头虎脑的男孩也跟着举手，差点从椅子上摔下来。全班都笑了。",
          "effects": [{ "type": "shake", "duration": 0.3 }]
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_7",
          "speaker": "teacher_wang",
          "speakerName": "王老师",
          "text": "好，那我们来投票。每个人只能选一个人哦。"
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_8",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "（要选谁呢？）",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text": "选小红 — 她看起来最有干劲",
              "jumpTo": "fw_9_hong",
              "actions": [{ "type": "affection", "key": "xiaohong", "value": 2 }, { "type": "affection", "key": "xiaoming", "value": -1 }]
            },
            {
              "text": "选小明 — 他很有趣",
              "jumpTo": "fw_9_ming",
              "actions": [{ "type": "affection", "key": "xiaoming", "value": 2 }]
            },
            {
              "text": "选青梅竹马 — 支持好朋友",
              "jumpTo": "fw_9_friend",
              "actions": [{ "type": "affection", "key": "childhood_friend", "value": 3 }]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_9_hong",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "我选小红。",
          "jumpTo": "fw_10"
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_9_ming",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "我选小明！",
          "jumpTo": "fw_10"
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_9_friend",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "我选我最好的朋友。",
          "jumpTo": "fw_10"
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_10",
          "speaker": "teacher_wang",
          "speakerName": "王老师",
          "text": "投票结果出来啦——小红当选班长！小明当副班长，你要帮班长维持纪律哦。",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_11",
          "speaker": "xiaoming",
          "speakerName": "小明",
          "text": "副班长？也行！以后谁敢捣乱，我就记他名字！",
          "emotion": "proud"
        },
        {
          "id": "fw_12",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "就这样，一年三班的班委产生了。我的小学生活也越来越热闹了。",
          "actions": [
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "class_leadership_elected" },
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "first_week_done" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ch1_midterm",
      "title": "期中考试 · 第一次测验",
      "background": "backgrounds/classroom_exam",
      "bgm": "bgm/focused_study",
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "id": "mt_1",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "开学一个多月了。今天是我人生中第一次期中考试。",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "hasFlag", "key": "first_week_done" }]
        },
        {
          "id": "mt_2",
          "speaker": "teacher_wang",
          "speakerName": "王老师",
          "text": "同学们不要紧张，这只是看看大家这个月学得怎么样。认真做题就好。",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "mt_3",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "卷子发下来了。第一题是拼音连线，第二题是十以内的加减法。",
          "effects": [{ "type": "fadeIn", "duration": 0.5 }]
        },
        {
          "id": "mt_4",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "（深呼吸…这些老师都教过，我能行的。）"
        },
        {
          "id": "mt_5",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "考试结束的铃声响了。我交上了卷子，手心都是汗。",
          "effects": [{ "type": "fadeOut", "duration": 0.5 }]
        },
        {
          "id": "mt_6",
          "speaker": "teacher_wang",
          "speakerName": "王老师",
          "text": "成绩出来啦！大家都考得很不错！特别表扬几位同学——",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "mt_7",
          "speaker": "xiaohong",
          "speakerName": "小红",
          "text": "（紧张地握紧拳头）",
          "emotion": "serious"
        },
        {
          "id": "mt_8",
          "speaker": "teacher_wang",
          "speakerName": "王老师",
          "text": "小红同学双科一百！值得表扬！",
          "emotion": "proud"
        },
        {
          "id": "mt_9",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "同学们都鼓起掌来。小红脸红了，害羞地低下了头。",
          "emotion": "shy"
        },
        {
          "id": "mt_10",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "（下次…我也要好好努力。）",
          "actions": [
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "first_exam_done" },
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "exam_ready" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ch1_sports_day",
      "title": "运动会 · 第一次合作",
      "background": "backgrounds/playground",
      "bgm": "bgm/sports_festival",
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "id": "sp_1",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "十月的运动会在秋高气爽中到来了。操场上到处是彩旗和加油声。",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "hasFlag", "key": "first_exam_done" }]
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_2",
          "speaker": "xiaoming",
          "speakerName": "小明",
          "text": "接力赛！接力赛！我们班一定拿第一！",
          "emotion": "proud"
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_3",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "小明是体育委员，他给大家安排了接力顺序。我被排在了第三棒。",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "hasFlag", "key": "protagonist_male" }]
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_3b",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "虽然有点紧张，但好朋友在旁边给我加油，让我安心了不少。",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "hasFlag", "key": "protagonist_female" }]
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_4",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "（接力棒好滑…可千万不能掉啊。）"
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_5",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "发令枪响。第一棒像箭一样冲了出去。第二棒接棒顺利。轮到我了。"
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_6",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "（来了！）"
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_7",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "我抓紧接力棒拼命往前跑。风在耳边呼呼地响。终点越来越近——",
          "effects": [{ "type": "zoomIn", "duration": 1.0 }]
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_8",
          "speaker": "xiaohong",
          "speakerName": "小红",
          "text": "加油！加油！",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_9",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "我把棒交给了最后一棒。他是全班跑得最快的同学。",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text": "冲到终点线旁边继续喊加油",
              "jumpTo": "sp_10_cheer",
              "actions": [{ "type": "affection", "key": "xiaoming", "value": 2 }, { "type": "setFlag", "key": "sports_enthusiasm" }]
            },
            {
              "text": "累得弯下腰喘气，但也在心里加油",
              "jumpTo": "sp_10_tired",
              "actions": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_10_cheer",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "加油！冲冲冲！！",
          "jumpTo": "sp_11"
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_10_tired",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "（加油…一定要赢…！）",
          "jumpTo": "sp_11"
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_11",
          "speaker": "teacher_wang",
          "speakerName": "王老师",
          "text": "一年三班——第二名！非常棒！大家都辛苦了！",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_12",
          "speaker": "xiaoming",
          "speakerName": "小明",
          "text": "第二名也不错！下次一定拿第一！",
          "emotion": "proud"
        },
        {
          "id": "sp_13",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "虽然没有拿到第一名，但大家一起加油的感觉真好。这大概就是「团队」的意义吧。",
          "actions": [
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "sports_day_done" },
            { "type": "affection", "key": "xiaoming", "value": 1 },
            { "type": "affection", "key": "xiaohong", "value": 1 }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ch1_semester_end",
      "title": "期末 · 第一学期结束",
      "background": "backgrounds/classroom_winter",
      "bgm": "bgm/winter_ending",
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "id": "se_1",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "时间过得很快。操场上的树叶落了又落，转眼间就到了期末。",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "hasFlag", "key": "sports_day_done" }],
          "effects": [{ "type": "fadeIn", "duration": 1.0 }]
        },
        {
          "id": "se_2",
          "speaker": "teacher_wang",
          "speakerName": "王老师",
          "text": "这个学期大家都表现得非常棒。每个人都比开学时进步了很多。",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "se_3",
          "speaker": "teacher_wang",
          "speakerName": "王老师",
          "text": "期末考试的试卷我已经发下去了。记得让家长签字，下学期开学带回来哦。"
        },
        {
          "id": "se_4",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "我看着试卷上的分数，虽然不如小红高，但比期中时进步了不少。自己觉得挺满意的。"
        },
        {
          "id": "se_5",
          "speaker": "xiaoming",
          "speakerName": "小明",
          "text": "耶！放假啦！！寒假我要天天去滑冰！",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "se_5b",
          "speaker": "childhood_friend",
          "speakerName": "小维",
          "text": "放假你会出来玩吗？我家附近新开了个公园，一起去吧？",
          "emotion": "happy",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "hasFlag", "key": "protagonist_male" }]
        },
        {
          "id": "se_5c",
          "speaker": "childhood_friend",
          "speakerName": "小康",
          "text": "放假有空吗？我买了新的跳绳，可以一起玩。",
          "emotion": "shy",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "hasFlag", "key": "protagonist_female" }]
        },
        {
          "id": "se_6",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "当然！",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text": "寒假一起好好学习",
              "jumpTo": "se_7_study",
              "actions": [{ "type": "setFlag", "key": "winter_study_plan" }, { "type": "affection", "key": "xiaohong", "value": 2 }]
            },
            {
              "text": "寒假一起好好玩",
              "jumpTo": "se_7_play",
              "actions": [{ "type": "setFlag", "key": "winter_play_plan" }, { "type": "affection", "key": "childhood_friend", "value": 2 }]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "se_7_study",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "但也要认真写作业。寒假作业好像有点多……",
          "jumpTo": "se_8"
        },
        {
          "id": "se_7_play",
          "speaker": "protagonist",
          "speakerName": "我",
          "text": "放假当然要好好玩！作业的事……之后再想！",
          "jumpTo": "se_8"
        },
        {
          "id": "se_8",
          "speaker": "teacher_wang",
          "speakerName": "王老师",
          "text": "同学们，寒假快乐！下学期见！",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "se_9",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "走出校门的时候，我回头看了一眼。一年级上学期就这样结束了。",
          "effects": [{ "type": "fadeOut", "duration": 1.5 }]
        },
        {
          "id": "se_10",
          "speaker": null,
          "speakerName": "",
          "text": "书包里装着试卷和奖状，心里装着一整个学期的回忆。",
          "effects": [{ "type": "fadeOut", "duration": 1.0 }],
          "actions": [
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "primary_1_semester_1_complete" },
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "first_semester_complete" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
